creator: BiblioCommons
descriptionHtml:
Keep a library in your pocket! St. Albert Public Library Mobile makes it easy to find and discover titles, manage your account, and get the library catalogue and availability information you need, anytime and anywhere.

Features:
· Quickly search the collection for books, movies, games, playaways, and more, with filters to zero-in on what you want
· get descriptions and community reviews for titles
· save titles to your ‘For Later’ list
· check availability
· instantly check your due dates and renew
· check if your holds are ready
· find and download eBooks and audiobooks
· browse bestsellers, new arrivals, and recent reviews
· rate titles with one touch
· check library hours or get directions to St. Albert Public Library
descriptionShort: Keep the St. Albert Public Library in your pocket!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: This is release includes behind the scenes changes, and small user interface adjustments.
